      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://noamelf.com/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Noam Elfanbaum</author>
      <guid>https://noamelf.com/about/</guid>
      <description></description>
      
      <content>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m Noam Elfanbaum, I live in Tel-Aviv with my wife, baby-daughter and dog.
I used to teach Python classes, do freelance work and organize Python community gatherings (&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.meetup.com/PyWeb-IL/&#34;&gt;PywebIL&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://il.pycon.org&#34;&gt;Pycon Israel&lt;/a&gt;). These days I&amp;rsquo;ve settled on a serious day job as a engineering team lead a Bluevine. Hope you enjoy the blog posts!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;center&#34;&gt;
